summary: A not so simple Imperial Preset for RaceMenu by Expired.
descriptionHtml:
[center][font=Courier New]
This preset is also a follower:[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/81337/?] [/url][/font][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/81337/?]Keira[/url][/center][center][font=Courier New]
Okay so..there are A LOT of requirements and recommended mods for this preset to be able to load properly as well as look as intended. 
[size=5]
[u][b][color=#ff0000]!!!!ABSOLUTE REQUIREMENTS!!!![/color][/b][/u][/size]
[url=http://http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url]
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RACEMENU[/url]
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363/?]KS HAIR HDT[/url]/or not
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty[/url]
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Eyebrows[/url]
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7127/?]RANs Head Mesh[/url] - C Variant
[u][color=#ff7700]
[size=5][b]EXTREMELY RECOMMENDED[/b][/size][/color][/u]
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49168/?]Eyebrow Specularity Fix[/url]
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60195/?]Merta Assassin Armor[/url] ([size=3][u]Tattoos)[/u][/size] (if you choose not to download any of the overlay mods this preset has, you may experience a "blue body," this can almost always be fixed by changing all body paint textures in the racemenu options to default)
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/48705/?]RaceMenu Overlay Compilation[/url]
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52841/?]Freckle Mania[/url]
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/73853/?]Pure Skin Textures[/url]
[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37900/?] UNPB body[/url] (I sculpted the neck  a little in order to fix a neck seam I was experiencing with the body, SOOOO if you don't use UNP body mods, be prepared for an awkward neck seam)
[b][u][size=4][color=#ffff00]
GRAPHICS USED IN SCREENSHOTS[/color]
[/size][/u][/b]
I use |[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/74552/?]Charlotte ENB[/url]| + |[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27043/?]ELFX[/url]| + |[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17802/?]COT[/url]| + |[url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61995/?]TR[/url]|
[/font]in addition to a huge number of misc. texture replacers.[/center]
author: JennaTheJew
